subSubSection.paragraph:
Diagnosis. Small or medium sized (
3.5–9.5 mm
) bright colored flies. Frons and face of medium width, vibrissal angle placed at oral margin, head in profile angular; hind border of head slightly shortened; 
orb
1+ 0–2; Postpedicel 3–10× as long as pedicel.
